---
import PerformanceCounter from './PerformanceCounter';
---
<section class="w-full py-16 md:py-32 px-4 md:px-12 bg-zinc-50 border-t border-zinc-200 text-primary">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-24 items-center">
        
        {/* 2. Visual X-Ray (Order 2 no Mobile, Coluna 1 no Desktop) */}
        {/* Removed md:row-span-2 since we are unifying the right column into a single cell */}
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 relative bg-white border-2 border-black p-5 md:p-10 shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] md:shadow-[12px_12px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] reveal-up transform md:-rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-all duration-500 rounded-2xl">
             {/* Fake Browser Header */}
             <div class="w-full flex items-center gap-1.5 mb-6 md:mb-8 pb-3 md:pb-4 border-b border-black/10">
                <div class="flex gap-1">
                    <div class="w-2 md:w-3 h-2 md:h-3 rounded-full bg-neutral-200 border border-black/10"></div>
                    <div class="w-2 md:w-3 h-2 md:h-3 rounded-full bg-neutral-200 border border-black/10"></div>
                    <div class="w-2 md:w-3 h-2 md:h-3 rounded-full bg-neutral-200 border border-black/10"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="ml-3 flex-1 h-3 bg-neutral-100 rounded-sm border border-black/5"></div>
             </div>

             {/* Scores Grid */}
             <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 md:gap-6">
                 <PerformanceCounter client:visible label="Performance" delay={0} />
                 <PerformanceCounter client:visible label="Acessibilidade" delay={200} />
                 <PerformanceCounter client:visible label="SEO" delay={400} />
             </div>

             {/* Technical Stamp */}
             <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-2 md:-right-3 bg-black text-white px-2 md:px-3 py-0.5 md:py-1 font-mono text-[8px] md:text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider transform rotate-3 shadow-md border border-white/20">
                Verificado via pagespeed insights
             </div>
        </div>

        {/* Desktop Wrapper for Title and Text (Col 2) */}
        {/* "contents" ensures children participate in main grid on Mobile, preserving gap-12 spacing without extra margins */}
        <div class="contents md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center md:gap-10 md:order-2">
            
            {/* 1. Título (Order 1 no Mobile inside wrapper) */}
            {/* NO margin-bottom here to avoid double gap on mobile */}
            <div class="order-1 md:order-none flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-serif leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-0 md:mb-0 reveal-up delay-100 mix-blend-multiply">
                    A velocidade é o <br>melhor <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-black to-neutral-500">posicionamento.</span>
                </h2>
            </div>
    
            {/* 3. Subtexto (Order 3 no Mobile inside wrapper) */}
            <div class="order-3 md:order-none flex flex-col justify-center text-center md:text-left items-center md:items-start">
                <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 text-black font-serif text-base md:text-xl leading-relaxed opacity-90">
                    <p class="reveal-text delay-200">
                        Um site que carrega em milissegundos não é apenas técnico; é uma estratégia de conversão que elimina a rejeição e gera maior retenção do público.
                    </p>
                    <p class="reveal-text delay-300">
                        Aqui, não sacrificamos a performance pela estética (nem o contrário). Construímos interfaces fluidas que respeitam o tempo do usuário.
                    </p>
                </div>
                 <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t-2 border-black/5 flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start items-center gap-3 md:gap-4 reveal-up delay-300">
                    <span class="font-mono text-[9px] md:text-xs uppercase bg-black text-white px-2 md:px-3 py-1">CONVERSAO_EXTREMA_V1.1</span>
                    <span class="font-mono text-[9px] md:text-xs uppercase text-neutral-500 font-bold">[ LCP: 0.4s ]</span>
                 </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</section>
